[Cite as 02121/2003 Case Announcements, 2003-Ohio-769.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 21, 2003

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2002-2224. Cuyahoga Cty. Bar Association v. McClain.

Upon consideration of relator’s motion for continuance of oral argument currently scheduled for February 25, 2003,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for continuance be, and hereby is, denied.
